法規內容.條文內容:
In applying for a transcription or transmission of the following information to be provided by the competent authority of the municipality directly under the jurisdiction of the Executive Yuan or the county (city) where the business is located, either in the form of computer print-out or electronic storage media provided by the applicant itself, the applicant shall pay a basic transcription fee in a fixed amount of NTD 5,000, provided however, that if the number of businesses whose information are to be copies (transcribed) exceeds 500, an extra transcription fee at the rate of NTD 10 per one additional business information shall be charged therefor:
1. the uniform serial number of the business;
2. the name of the business;
3. the organization of the business;
4. the scope of business;
5. the amount of capital;
6. the location of the business;
7. the name of the responsible person;
8. the names of the partners, if in the form of partnership; and
9. the date of approval of its establishment.
